# Mini-Adventure

This is a simple text adventure made using python.

Its very simple to use just follow the on screen instructions.

## Future tasks

1. Add even more enemys

2. Add items eg. Health Potion

3. Use level, and attack to work out damage. Then knock down for the defence.

4. Add a bag for player to hold items

5. Add random items drops for when a enemy is defeated

